'''Skylight Squadron''' was a unit of modified, [[Deflector shield/Legends|shield]]-equipped [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]] assigned to the [[Flight group/Legends|flight]] complement of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] [[Allegiance (Imperial I-class)|''Allegiance'']]. This unit fought in the [[Battle of Adumar]] [[12 ABY/Legends|twelve years after]] the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], and were part of the force that attacked the [[TIE/d "Defender" Multi-Role Starfighter/Legends|TIE Defenders]] of the [[181st Imperial Fighter Wing/Legends|181st Imperial Fighter Wing]].

Unfortunately, the units own TIEs were no match for the Defenders of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] invasion [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]]. It took [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]' [[Red Flight]] to successfully engage and fight off the Defender unit.

